Commented on #706 OWASP Nest Kubernetes Adoption

Hi @arkid15r I am interested in this idea. I work as a DevOps Engineer at Oracle and have good experience with Kubernetes, cloud platforms, Grafana, CI/CD, and related technologies. I was checking out issue https://github.com/OWASP/Nest/issues/706, where you highlighted the plan and steps. We should discuss about 1 (planning and architecture) and 2 (k8s setup).
I tried exploring a bit for k8s setup and have a "basic" working version here in my fork - jaiakash/Nest@k8s-deployement with yaml configs for backend (Django), frontend (React), and db. I am about setup github action to build and publish to GCR And to deploy using my personal Amazon EKS account Finally, to set up Prometheus and Grafana for metrics.
The fork contains an experimental version, which I am trying to assess and experiment with. Could you give me feedback on it? I will post my findings here in the discussion.
